    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_6080328263240114028.png",
                "id": "talent70719",
                "key": "Cloud-Grazing Strike ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cloud-Grazing Strike "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Flying Cloud Flag Formation</span>, attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield of Swirling Clouds</span> to this character and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prepare Skill</span>: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Spear Flourish</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Flying Cloud Flag Formation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your character uses a Normal Attack:</span> If you have no more than 1 card in your Hand, this Skill costs 1 less Elemental Die.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 4 stacks)<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield of Swirling Clouds</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>While preparing this Skill: Grant 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield</span> points to the character to which this is attached.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Spear Flourish</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. If you have <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span>ed or used at least 1 card for <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tune</span> this Round, this deals +1 DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/b7b312b24d3122cbdc5697f8f6f8dd71_4202847480263589876.png",
                "id": "talent17285",
                "key": "Opening Flourish",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Opening Flourish"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, creates 3 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Flying Cloud Flag Formation</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Flying Cloud Flag Formation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your character uses a Normal Attack:</span> If you have no more than 1 card in your Hand, this Skill costs 1 less Elemental Die.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 4 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/a63a85773eeaa24ce61231eec6b6dd10_3626456131375384002.png",
                "id": "talent81505",
                "key": "Cliffbreaker's Banner",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cliffbreaker's Banner"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_7500050857890900093.png",
                "id": "talent28039",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong><br>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Prepare Skill</span></strong><br>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span> over a certain number of turns.<br>When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> cannot activate effects triggered by \"using a Skill\" or \"triggering an Elemental Reaction\" or other such effects.)<br>Only active characters can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare</span> Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation</span> will be interrupted.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Tune</span></strong><br>Discard Action Cards from Hand to initiate Elemental Tuning</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1260738839980866919.png",
                "id": "talent4127",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
